{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810670/extras/HeaderGIF.gif?t=1738071989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cat Detective Albert Wilde</strong> is a 1930s noir-inspired detective game with humanoid animal characters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">How does Albert Wilde solve the strangest quantum mystery in a murder case? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find out in this 6-7 hours silly and hilarious classic detective adventure tribute to the golden age of noir movies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810670/extras/Interrogate.png?t=1738071989\" />Use your years of experience of interrogating and drinking at bars to chat with locals to solve a mystery. Rely on your cat-charisma to find the truth.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810670/extras/Butt.png?t=1738071989\" />Meet a cast of 27 interesting characters like a pole-dancing flamingo, a piggy lawyer, a pissed-off moose bookie, an out-of-tune sheep singer, a FAMOUS SCIENTIST and the dangerous crocodile gang. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810670/extras/Cat.png?t=1738071989\" />Albert Wilde is down on his luck. He\u2019s broke, he\u2019s friendless, he can\u2019t get a girl, and his landlord won\u2019t let him pee on the office wall anymore.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810670/extras/FooterGIF_1.gif?t=1738071989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Q &amp; A</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Is the game a combination of different genres?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Yes, it\u2019s hard to define <i>Cat Detective Albert Wilde</i> by a single genre, as we tend to blend multiple elements in our projects. This game is a fusion of comedy, film noir, detective mystery, science fiction, and narrative.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Can you describe the genre from a technical perspective?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From a technical perspective, you could describe it as something between a walking simulator and an interactive novel, with a strong emphasis on comedy.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Is this game a kind of \u2018whodunnit\u2019 murder mystery game?\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s less of a typical &quot;whodunnit&quot; and more of an origin story\u2014showing how Albert Wilde evolves from a Private Investigator (P.I.) to a Quantum Private Investigator.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Case","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1810670/b463fc9f83e6ea85b1a261ae3117b47b37c1c5c9.jpg"},{"name":"Dance","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1810670/5ff5bb2c92fdcad12e921b72633e9cb605dc0f89.jpg"},{"name":"The Sewers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1810670/095fa41e57aef18dcaf3351de09cbfd77e103493.jpg"},{"name":"Back Cover","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1810670/7c55f9ae6c783071ad6e0458e2ddbc73c4812b4b.jpg"},{"name":"The Password","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1810670/dc45dc2276e5a253a59ff280baf01bb396111dea.jpg"},{"name":"Scales","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1810670/a8471e2b07c8ecc06955c3b49d6ea0d8fdc91fcc.jpg"},{"name":"The Arc