rt Wilde</i> by a single genre, as we tend to blend multiple elements in our projects. This game is a fusion of comedy, film noir, detective mystery, science fiction, and narrative.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Can you describe the genre from a technical perspective?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From a technical perspective, you could describe it as something between a walking simulator and an interactive novel, with a strong emphasis on comedy.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Is this game a kind of \u2018whodunnit\u2019 murder mystery game?\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s less of a typical &quot;whodunnit&quot; and more of an origin story\u2014showing how Albert Wilde evolves from a Private Investigator (P.I.) to a Quantum Private Investigator.</p>","developers":["beyondthosehills"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810670/header.jpg?t=1738071989","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257088866,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257088866/movie480.mp4?t=1737723801","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257088866/movie_max.mp4?t=1737723801"},"name":"Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257088866/1e384b53c848095fb4fc58065f64532a6747f040/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1737723801","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257088866/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1737723801","max":"http://vi